msgstr ""
"Para ello, vaya a :menuselection:`Inventario --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Ajustes`, "
"busque la secciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Cﺣﺏdigo de barras` y seleccione la casilla junto "
"a la opciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Lector de cﺣﺏdigo de barras`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/transfers_scratch.rst:22
msgid ""
"Once the checkbox is ticked, click :guilabel:`Save` at the top of the page "
"to save changes."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que la casilla estﺣ۸ marcada, haga clic en :guilabel:`Guardar` en la "
"parte superior de la pﺣ۰gina para guardar los cambios."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:33
msgid ""
"After saving, a new drop-down menu appears under the :guilabel:`Barcode "
"Scanner` option, labeled :guilabel:`Barcode Nomenclature`, where "
"either :guilabel:`Default Nomenclature` or :guilabel:`Default GS1 "
