#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:67
msgid ""
"To begin the adjustment, first scan the *source location*, which is the "
"current location in the warehouse of the product whose count should be "
"adjusted. Then, scan the product barcode(s)."
msgstr ""
"Para iniciar el ajuste, primero escanee la *ubicaciﺣﺏn de origen*, que es la "
"ubicaciﺣﺏn actual en el almacﺣ۸n del producto cuyo recuento debe ajustarse. A "
"continuaciﺣﺏn, escanee el cﺣﺏdigo o cﺣﺏdigos de barras del producto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:70
msgid ""
"The barcode of a specific product can be scanned multiple times to increase "
"the quantity of that product in the adjustment."
msgstr ""
"Puede escanear el cﺣﺏdigo de barras de un producto especﺣ­fico varias veces "
"para aumentar la cantidad de ese producto en el ajuste."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:74
msgid ""
"If the warehouse *multi-location* feature is **not** enabled in the "
"database, a source location does not need to be scanned. Instead, simply "
"scan the product barcode to start the inventory adjustment."
msgstr ""
"No es necesario que escanee una ubicaciﺣﺏn de origen si la funciﺣﺏn "
"*Ubicaciones mﺣﭦltiples* del almacﺣ۸n **no** estﺣ۰ activada en la base de "
"datos. Escanee el cﺣﺏdigo de barras del producto para iniciar el ajuste del "
"inventario."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:78
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the quantity can be changed by clicking the :guilabel:`ﻗﺅﺕ "
"(pencil)` icon on the far right of the product line."
msgstr ""
"Tambiﺣ۸n puede hacer clic en el icono :guilabel:`ﻗﺅﺕ (lﺣ۰piz)` a la derecha de "
"la lﺣ­nea de producto para cambiar la cantidad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:81
msgid ""
"Doing so opens a separate window with a keypad. Edit the number in "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` line to change the quantity. Additionally, "
"the :guilabel:`+1` and :guilabel:`-1` buttons can be clicked to add or "
"subtract quantity of the product, and the number keys can be used to add "
"quantity, as well."
msgstr ""
"Esta acciﺣﺏn abre otra ventana con un teclado numﺣ۸rico. Edite el nﺣﭦmero en la "
"lﺣ­nea :guilabel:`Cantidad` para cambiarla. Ademﺣ۰s, puede hacer clic en "
"botones :guilabel:`+1` y :guilabel:`-1` para agregar o restar cantidad del "
"producto. Tambiﺣ۸n puede usar las teclas numﺣ۸ricas para aﺣﺎadir cantidad."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:86
msgid ""
"In the below inventory adjustment, the source location `WH/Stock/Shelf/2` "
"was scanned, assigning the location. Then, the barcode for the product "
"`[FURN_7888] Desk Stand with Screen` was scanned 3 times, increasing the "
"units in the adjustment. Additional products can be added to this adjustment "
"by scanning the barcodes for those specific products."
msgstr ""
"En el siguiente ajuste de inventario se escaneﺣﺏ la ubicaciﺣﺏn de origen `WH/"
"Stock/Shelf/2` para asignar la ubicaciﺣﺏn. Despuﺣ۸s se escaneﺣﺏ el cﺣﺏdigo de "
"barras del producto `[FURN_7888] Soporte de escritorio con pantalla` tres "
"veces para aumentar las unidades del ajuste. Es posible agregar mﺣ۰s "
"productos a este ajuste al escanear los cﺣﺏdigos de barras de esos productos "
"en especﺣ­fico."

