#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/gs1_usage.rst:10
msgid ""
"GS1 barcodes provide a standardized format that barcode scanners can "
"interpret. They encode information in a :ref:`specific structure recognized "
"globally <barcode/operations/gs1>`, allowing scanners to understand and "
"process supply chain data consistently."
msgstr ""
"Los cﺣﺏdigos de barras GS1 ofrecen un formato estandarizado que los lectores "
"de cﺣﺏdigos de barras pueden interpretar. Codifican la informaciﺣﺏn en "
"una :ref:`estructura especﺣ­fica reconocida a nivel internacional <barcode/"
"operations/gs1>`, lo que permite que los lectores entiendan y procesen los "
"datos de la cadena de suministro de forma uniforme."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/gs1_usage.rst:14
msgid ""
"Odoo *Barcode* interprets and prints GS1 barcodes, automating product "
"identification and tracking in warehouse operations such as receiving, "
"picking, and shipping."
msgstr ""
"*Cﺣﺏdigo de barras* de Odoo interpreta e imprime los cﺣﺏdigos de barras GS1 y "
"de esa manera se automatiza la identificaciﺣﺏn y rastreo de productos en las "
"operaciones de almacﺣ۸n como la recepciﺣﺏn, la recolecciﺣﺏn y el envﺣ­o. "

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/gs1_usage.rst:17
msgid ""
"The following sections contain examples of how Odoo uses GS1 barcodes "
"provided by the business to identify common warehouse items and automate "
"certain warehouse workflows."
msgstr ""
"Las siguientes secciones contienen ejemplos de cﺣﺏmo Odoo usa los cﺣﺏdigos de "
"barras GS1 que proporcionan los negocios para identificar artﺣ­culos en comﺣﭦn "
"en los almacenes y automatiza ciertos flujos de trabajo del almacﺣ۸n. "

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/gs1_usage.rst:21
msgid ""
"Odoo **does not** create GS1 barcodes. Businesses must purchase a unique "
"Global Trade Item Number (GTIN) from GS1. Then, they can combine their "
"existing GS1 barcodes with product and supply chain information (also "
"provided by GS1) to create barcodes in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **no** crea cﺣﺏdigos de barras GS1. Las empresas deben adquirir un "
"nﺣﭦmero global de artﺣ­culo comercial (GTIN) de GS1. Luego, podrﺣ۰n combinar "
"sus cﺣﺏdigos de barras GS1 existentes con un producto y la informaciﺣﺏn de la "
"cadena de suministro (que tambiﺣ۸n proporciona GS1) para crear cﺣﺏdigos de "
"barras en Odoo. "

