#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:22
msgid "Barcode formats"
msgstr "Formatos de cﺣﺏdigos de barras"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is possible to use *default nomenclature* for the barcodes in the "
"database. Default nomenclature supports barcode actions using product "
"universal product codes (UPCs) and European Article Number (EAN) barcodes."
msgstr ""
"Puedes usar la *nomenclatura predeterminada* para los cﺣﺏdigos de barras en "
"la base de datos. La nomenclatura predeterminada admite acciones de cﺣﺏdigos "
"de barras que usan cﺣﺏdigos universales de producto (UPC) y cﺣﺏdigos de barras "
"de nﺣﭦmero de artﺣ­culo internacional (EAN)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:28
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use *default GS1 nomenclature*. GS1 nomenclature "
"consolidates various product and supply chain data into a single barcode. "
"Most retail products use EAN-13 barcodes, also known as GTIN (Global Trade "
"Identification Numbers). GTINs are used by companies to uniquely identify "
"their products and services. While GTIN and UPC are often used synonymously, "
"GTIN refers to the number a barcode represents, while UPC refers to the "
"barcode itself. More information about GTINs can be found on the `GS1 "
"website <https://www.gs1.org/standards/get-barcodes>`__."
msgstr ""
"Tambiﺣ۸n puedes usar la *nomenclatura GS1 predeterminada*. La nomenclatura "
"GS1 consolida distintos datos de productos y de la cadena de suministro en "
"un solo cﺣﺏdigo de barras. La mayorﺣ­a de los productos de venta al por menor "
"usan cﺣﺏdigos de barras EAN-13, tambiﺣ۸n conocidos como cﺣﺏdigo comercial "
"global de artﺣ­culo. Los cﺣﺏdigos comerciales globales de artﺣ­culo permiten "
"que las empresas identifiquen de forma ﺣﭦnica sus productos y servicios. "
"Aunque el cﺣﺏdigo comercial global de artﺣ­culo y el UPC suelen usarse como "
"sinﺣﺏnimos, el cﺣﺏdigo comercial global de artﺣ­culo representa el nﺣﭦmero que "
"representa un cﺣﺏdigo de barras, mientras que el UPC representa al cﺣﺏdigo de "
"barras en sﺣ­. Puedes encontrar mﺣ۰s informaciﺣﺏn sobre los cﺣﺏdigos comerciales "
"globales de artﺣ­culo en el `sitio web de GS1 <https://www.gs1.org/standards/"
"get-barcodes>`__."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:35
msgid ""
"In order to create GTINs for items, a company must have a GS1 company "
"prefix. This prefix is the number that appears at the beginning of each "
"GTIN, and identifies the company as the owner of the barcode. To learn more "
"about GS1 company prefixes, or purchase a license for a prefix, visit the "
"`GS1 Company Prefix <https://www.gs1.org/standards/id-keys/company-"
"prefix>`__ page."
msgstr ""
"Para crear cﺣﺏdigos comerciales globales de artﺣ­culo para los artﺣ­culos, una "
"empresa debe tener un prefijo de empresa GS1. Este prefijo es el nﺣﭦmero que "
"aparece al inicio de cada cﺣﺏdigo comercial global de artﺣ­culo e identifica a "
"la empresa como propietaria del cﺣﺏdigo de barras. Para obtener mﺣ۰s "
"informaciﺣﺏn sobre los prefijos de empresa GS1 o comprar una licencia para un "
"prefijo, visita la pﺣ۰gina de `prefijo de empresa GS1 <https://www.gs1.org/"
"standards/id-keys/company-prefix>`__."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:41
msgid ""
"Odoo supports GTIN barcodes to identify products. However, since Odoo "
