"ser :guilabel:`Producto almacenable`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:57
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Traceability` section. From here, make sure that "
"either :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number` or :guilabel:`By Lots` is checked."
