"caducidad para bienes que ingrese a sus existencias, no importa si los "
"comprﺣﺏ a un proveedor o si usted los fabricﺣﺏ."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once all the expiration information has been configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
