"las :guilabel:`ﺣﺏrdenes de envﺣ­o` desde la "
"aplicaciﺣﺏn :menuselection:`Inventario`, :ref:`agregue al transportista "
"externo <inventory/shipping_receiving/validate-print-label>` en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Transportista` y valide la orden de entrega."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:82
msgid "Add shipping on quotation"
msgstr "Agregar el envﺣ­o a la cotizaciﺣﺏn"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:84
