"seguridad tambiﺣ۸n establece un margen que toma en cuenta las posibles "
"demoras en las entregas de los proveedores. Haga clic en :guilabel:`Guardar`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:228
msgid ""
"Setting the :guilabel:`Security Lead Time for Purchase` to `2.00` days, "
"pushes the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` of receipt back by two days. In that "
