#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:384
msgid ""
"Odoo's replenishment planning maps a business' order fulfillment process, "
"setting pre-determined deadlines and raw material order dates, including "
"buffer days for potential delays. This ensures products are delivered on "
"time."
msgstr ""
"La planeaciﺣﺏn de reabastecimiento de Odoo trasforma el proceso de "
"cumplimiento de ﺣﺏrdenes de una empresa, establece plazos predefinidos y "
"fechas para ordenar materia prima, ademﺣ۰s incluye dﺣ­as con un margen en caso "
