#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:99
msgid ":guilabel:`Product`: The product that requires replenishment."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Producto`: El producto que debe reabastecer."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Location`: The specific location where the product is stored."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ubicaciﺣﺏn`: La ubicaciﺣﺏn especﺣ­fica de almacenamiento del "
"producto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Min Quantity`: The minimum amount of product that should be "
"available. When inventory levels goes below this number, the replenishment "
"is triggered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cantidad mﺣ­nima`: La cantidad mﺣ­nima de producto que deberﺣ­a "
"estar disponible. El reabastecimiento se activa cuando los niveles de "
"inventario estﺣ۰n por debajo de este nﺣﭦmero."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max Quantity`: The amount of product that should be available "
"after replenishing the product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cantidad mﺣ۰xima`: La cantidad de producto que deberﺣ­a estar "
"disponible despuﺣ۸s de reabastecer el producto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Multiple Quantity`: Ensures products are replenished in fixed "
"multiples, rounding the ordered quantity up to the nearest multiple that "
"meets or slightly exceeds the :guilabel:`Max Quantity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cantidad mﺣﭦltiple`: Garantiza el reabastecimiento de productos en "
"mﺣﭦltiplos fijos y redondea la cantidad ordenada al mﺣﭦltiplo mﺣ۰s cercano que "
"alcance o supere ligeramente la :guilabel:`cantidad mﺣ۰xima`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:109
msgid ""
"For example, if :guilabel:`Multiple Quantity` is `3`, products are ordered "
"in multiples of three (3, 6, 9, ...). If the :guilabel:`Max Quantity` is "
"`20` and the forecasted quantity is `7`, the required quantity is `13`. "
"Because `13` is not a multiple of three, Odoo rounds up and orders `15`."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, si :guilabel:`cantidad mﺣﭦltiple` es `3`, Odoo ordena los "
"productos en mﺣﭦltiplos de tres (3, 6, 9...). Si la :guilabel:`cantidad "
"mﺣ۰xima` es `20` y la cantidad pronosticada es `7`, la cantidad requerida es "
"`13`. Como `13` no es mﺣﭦltiplo de tres, Odoo redondea hacia arriba y ordena "
"`15`."

