"utilizando la ruta seleccionada que aparece en primer lugar en la "
"pestaﺣﺎa :guilabel:`Inventario` del formulario del producto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:318
msgid "Advanced uses"
msgstr "Usos avanzados"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:320
msgid ""
"Pairing :guilabel:`Preferred Route` with one of the following fields on the "
"replenishment report unlocks advanced configurations of reordering rules. "
"Consider the following:"
msgstr ""
"Usar la :guilabel:`ruta preferida` con uno de los siguientes campos del "
"reporte de reabastecimiento le permite usar configuraciones avanzadas en las "
"reglas de reordenamiento. Considere lo siguiente:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:325
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`: When the selected :guilabel:`Preferred Route` "
"is :guilabel:`Buy`, setting the :guilabel:`Vendor` field to one of the "
"multiple vendors on the vendor pricelist indicates to Odoo that the vendor "
"is automatically populated on |RFQs| when a reordering rule triggers the "
"creation of a purchase order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Proveedor`: Cuando la :guilabel:`ruta preferida` "
"es :guilabel:`Comprar`, configurar el campo :guilabel:`Proveedor` con uno de "
"los que se encuentran en la lista de precios de proveedores le indica a Odoo "
"que el proveedor se completarﺣ۰ de forma automﺣ۰tica en las solicitudes de "
"cotizaciﺣﺏn cuando una regla de reordenamiento activa la creaciﺣﺏn de una "
"orden de compra."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:332
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill of Materials`: When the :guilabel:`Preferred Route` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Manufacture`, and there are multiple |BoMs| in use, specifying "
"the desired |BoM| in the replenishment report, draft manufacturing orders "
"are created with this |BoM| in use."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lista de materiales`: Cuando la :guilabel:`ruta preferida` "
"es :guilabel:`Fabricaciﺣﺏn` y hay varias listas de materiales en uso, al "
"especificar la lista de materiales en el reporte de reabastecimiento, los "
"borradores de las ﺣﺏrdenes de fabricaciﺣﺏn se crearﺣ۰n con esa lista."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:338
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Procurement Group`: This is a way to group related |POs| or |MOs| "
"that are tied to fulfilling a specific demand, like an |SO| or a project. It "
"helps organize and track which orders are linked to a particular demand."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Grupo de aprovisionamiento`: Esta es una forma de agrupar ﺣﺏrdenes "
"de compra y fabricaciﺣﺏn que estﺣ۰n relacionadas con el cumplimiento de una "
"demanda especﺣ­fica, como una orden de venta o proyecto. Ayuda a organizar y "
"rastrear quﺣ۸ ﺣﺏrdenes estﺣ۰n vinculadas a una demanda en particular."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:343
msgid ""
"Procurement groups link replenishment methods to demand, enabling smart "
"buttons to appear when using the :doc:`MTO route <mto>`."
msgstr ""
"Los grupos de aprovisionamiento vinculan los mﺣ۸todos de reabastecimiento con "
"la demanda, lo que hace que aparezcan botones inteligentes al usar "
"la :doc:`ruta de fabricaciﺣﺏn sobre pedido <mto>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:0
msgid "Showing smart button to PO."
msgstr "Botﺣﺏn inteligente en la orden de compra."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:349
msgid ""
"Sales order (demand) with a linked purchase order (replenishment method)."
msgstr ""
"Orden de venta (demanda) con una orden de compra vinculada (mﺣ۸todo de "
"reabastecimiento),"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:351
msgid "In the context of reordering rules:"
msgstr "En el contexto de las reglas de reabastecimiento:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:353
msgid ""
"Reordering rules do not automatically assign a procurement group, which is "
"why there are no smart buttons that link |SOs| to |POs|, unlike "
"the :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)` route."
msgstr ""
"Las reglas de reabastecimiento no asignan un grupo de aprovisionamiento de "
"forma automﺣ۰tica, por lo que no hay botones inteligentes que vinculen "
"ﺣﺏrdenes de venta a ﺣﺏrdenes de compra, contrario a la ruta fabricaciﺣﺏn sobre "
"pedido."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:355
msgid ""
"To enable smart buttons for products replenished by reordering rules "
"(not :abbr:`MTO (Make to Order)`), with specific quantities linked to "
"specific demands (e.g. |SOs|), assign a procurement group."
msgstr ""
"Para activar los botones inteligentes para productos que se reabastecen con "
"reglas de reabastecimiento (que no sea fabricaciﺣﺏn sobre pedido), con "
"cantidades especﺣ­ficas vinculadas a demandas especﺣ­ficas (por ejemplo, "
"ﺣﺏrdenes de venta) asigne un grupo de aprovisionamiento."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:358
msgid ""
"Without a procurement group, demands for the same product can be combined "
"into a single |RFQ|, even if the reordering rule is executed multiple times "
"for those demands. This allows for more efficient procurement by "
"consolidating demands into fewer orders."
msgstr ""
"Sin un grupo de aprovisionamiento, las demandas para el mismo producto "
"pueden combinarse en una misma solicitud de cotizaciﺣﺏn, incluso si la regla "
"de reabastecimiento se ejecuta varias veces para esas demandas. Asﺣ­ es "
"posible contar con un aprovisionamiento mﺣ۰s eficaz ya que consolidamos las "
"mismas demandas en menos ﺣﺏrdenes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:362
msgid ""
"Selecting a procurement group in the :guilabel:`Procurement Group` field on "
"the replenishment report ensures that all linked orders are grouped under "
"the same demand, based on the defined route."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionar un grupo de aprovisionamiento en el campo :guilabel:`Grupo de "
"aprovisionamiento` en el reporte de reabastecimiento se asegura que todas "
"las ﺣﺏrdenes vinculadas estﺣ۸n agrupadas en la misma demanda, segﺣﭦn la ruta "
"definida."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:367
msgid ""
"How can you set the *Procurement Group*, *Vendor*, and *Preferred Route* "
"fields on the replenishment report to generate a single |RFQ| for five "
