msgstr ""
"Para acceder a y gestionar los tipos de ECO debe ir a la "
"aplicaciﺣﺏn :menuselection:`PLM --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Tipos de ﺣﺏrdenes de "
"cambio de ingenierﺣ­a`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/plm/manage_changes/eco_type.rst:28
msgid ""
"Create a new ECO type by clicking :guilabel:`New`. On the new :guilabel:`ECO "
