#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/plm/manage_changes/eco_type.rst:51
msgid ""
"On the form for each |ECO| type, proceed to edit the :guilabel:`Name` "
"and :guilabel:`Email Alias` fields."
msgstr ""
"Edita los campos :guilabel:`Nombre` y :guilabel:`Alias de correo` en el "
