"pestaﺣﺎa :guilabel:`Crear alternativa`, haga clic en :guilabel:`Comparar "
"lﺣ­neas de producto` que le redirigirﺣ۰ a la pﺣ۰gina :guilabel:`Comparar lﺣ­neas "
"de orden`. "

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/calls_for_tenders.rst:None
