"Esta acciﺣﺏn abre el formulario de devoluciﺣﺏn. En la parte superior de este "
"formulario ahora aparece el botﺣﺏn inteligente :guilabel:`ﺣrdenes de "
"reparaciﺣﺏn` que vincula esta devoluciﺣﺏn a la orden de reparaciﺣﺏn completada."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:246
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Return` at the top of the form. This opens "
"a :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en :guilabel:`Devolver` en la parte superior del formulario para "
"abrir la ventana emergente :guilabel:`Revertir traslado`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/repairs/repair_orders.rst:262
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Return` to confirm the return. This creates a "
"new delivery for the returned products."
msgstr ""
"Luego haga clic en :guilabel:`Devolver` para confirmar la devoluciﺣﺏn. Esto "
